    "actor_description": "My body responds before I can argue with it—heat low in my belly, breath tightening, attention snapping to every nerve. And then shame rushes in like a spotlight: Not this. Not like this. Not me. I try to shut it down by sheer will—by looking away, by holding still, by thinking of anything else—while the wanting keeps pressing forward under my skin, stubborn and alive.",
